Synopsis: Nested dialogue. After impersonating a member of the player's camp (in camp or on entering the undercity), Orin reveals herself and delivers an ultimatum to the player: kill Gortash, or she will kill the abductee. Dark Urge players receive an alternate flow, where their shared background and rivalry is more present.
